Data Analyst Position - TechCorp

We are looking for a skilled Data Analyst to join our team.

REQUIREMENTS:
• 3+ years experience in data analysis
• Proficiency in SQL, Python, and Power BI
• Experience with machine learning and predictive analytics
• Strong analytical and problem-solving skills
• Experience with business intelligence tools
• Knowledge of data visualization and dashboard creation

RESPONSIBILITIES:
• Analyze large datasets to identify trends and insights
• Create and maintain interactive dashboards
• Develop predictive models for business forecasting
• Collaborate with stakeholders to understand business requirements
• Present findings to management and stakeholders
title: Data Analyst
